cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning, specifically with contextualized word embeddings and their interpretability. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves machine learning algorithms and techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper deals with the optimization of embeddings, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which makes cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
